snippet.title: Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Cloudy Super Mario Bros U is a mod of New Super Mario Bros U, which has now been released!
This mod features:
-30 completely new stages, each having a unique theming
-A bunch of new tilesets

Download:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Sip7ErRhFGfqG5VndD6u5rFZ3z5R3u0e/

► NSMBWii / NSMBU Modding Discord: https://discord.gg/aZAaXVJ
